What Are Minecoins? Minecoins are the official currency used in Minecraft. It’s a golden coin with an “M” logo on it. Whenever you et Minecoins, it is assigned to your Xbox Live account. Minecoins are the same as Minecraft tokens(for PS4 players). However, this is only available for the Bedrock edition of the game.

Minecraft is a massive game and it’s perfect for creative people. You can create your own interesting worlds with it. Some people create custom skins and texture mods for the game. The Minecraft marketplace lets the player share these creations with others for a certain amount of Minecoins.

Officially, there are no ways to get free Minecoins and you have to purchase them with real money. However, if you are looking for free Minecoins, then do not worry, we have your back. Just to be clear, we are not going to cover any Minecoin generators, they are scams and we will cover them later on in this article.
